title: A 5.0 Manifesto
author: Endergun
pages:
#- A 5.0 Manifesto§0
§0-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-A summary of concepts for consideration in future iterations of the CivClassics server.
#- Reinforcement§0
§0-------------------* Remove reinforcement groups, have all reinforcements be equal to all players regardless of who reinforces.§0
§0* Match maturation times with current acid times.
#- * Chests become locked by assigning them to renamed papers, opening a locked chest requires having the paper in inventory.§0
§0* Replace acid with "solvent", expensive item that takes up resources for effectively doing the /ctb command.
#- * Solvents would be roughly in resource value to their corrosponding reinforcement material, requires mass resources in factories to make.§0
§0* Destroys reinforcement material in use.
#- Farming§0
§0-------------------* Double all crop times.
#- Bastions§0
§0-------------------* Remove them.
#- Map Generation§0
§0-------------------* Remove a large chunk of nether islands, situate them further to the map fringes.§0
§0* Larger, uninterrupted land masses, larger biomes, less rivers in favour of fewer, longer ones.§0

#- * Divide map between a small few continents, spread between oceans, each reasonably consistent in biomes, less or more of each kind.§0
§0* More seas, gulfs, basins.§0
§0* Mountain ranges dividing areas of a continent.
#- * Square pyramid-like structures of bedrock underneath large mountains such as in ranges.§0
§0* Surplus and deficit of iron and diamonds veins in certain regions, heavier distribution near mountain ranges.
#- * Allow certain lakes and basins to go below or above sea level.§0
§0* 20km radius.§0
§0* Man-made structures (a la dungeons but bigger) in world on spawn with loot, reinforced with stone, very rare.
#- Snitches§0
§0-------------------* Snitch messages disabled outside a 2km radius of the snitch.§0
§0* Similar locking mechanism to chests as previously mentioned.
#- General§0
§0-------------------* No direct messaging or group chats.§0
§0* Disable pearl and chorus fruit teleports.
#- 